    "Likewise, the dimensions can be utilized to systematically evaluate the effectiveness of tools.",
    "As such, our framework could be useful to system designers in both a conceptual and operational phase of tool production.",
    "Evaluation of tools is especially important as they come with certain limitations and can potentially produce side effects, depending on the usage scenario.",
    "The use of simulation tools like Bad News, GoViral!, and Fake It To Make It places players in the role of a disinformation website editor, helping them to understand the mechanisms behind creating and spreading fraudulent content.",
